Name: Black Walnut
Description: A wallnut with a earthier taste. Their shells are thick, tough to crack, and will likely stain your hands.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Una nuez con un sabor terroso. Tus conchas son gruesas, difíciles de romper y probablemente manchen sus manos.
DescriptionLocalization.zh: 带有泥土味道的核桃。它们的外壳很厚，非常难开，可能弄脏你的双手。
